    "body": "The gas price oracle will ignore transactions below the price configured by `--gpo.ignoreprice`, and the default value of that option is slightly above zero. You can try setting this to zero, but I'm not sure whether that will make it suggest a price of zero.\r\n\r\nIn general, the gas price oracle is not designed to work well in an environment where transactions can be submitted with zero fee.",
